<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-cash-flow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="528"><p sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-cash-flow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="528">Select <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-cash-flow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="528">New</strong> to create a record, and specify a name and description for the journal.</p>
