<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-cash-flow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="577"><p sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-cash-flow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="577">Select <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-cash-flow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="577">Edit beginning balance</strong> to change the beginning balance of this journal.</p>
