<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-cash-flow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="578"><p sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-cash-flow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="578">For lines that have <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-cash-flow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="578">Payment request</strong> as the journal data source, select <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-cash-flow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="578">Payment request lines</strong> to review the payment request lines that are included on the current journal line.</p>
</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-cash-flow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="579"><p sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-cash-flow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="579">Close the page.</p>
