<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-cash-flow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="580"><p sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-cash-flow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="580">On the <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-cash-flow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="580">Payment schedule journal</strong> page, select <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-cash-flow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="580">Payment schedule</strong> to review the payment schedule sheet. If a cash shortage or surplus is detected and should be prevented, you can make changes.</p>
