<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-cash-flow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="585"><p sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-cash-flow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="585">Set the <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-cash-flow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="585">Show totals per method of payments</strong> option to <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-cash-flow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="585">Yes</strong> if the payment schedule sheet should be calculated based on methods of payments.</p>
