<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-cash-flow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="586"><p sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-cash-flow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="586">Use the right arrow button (<strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-cash-flow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="586">&gt;</strong>) to select an aggregation parameter for the payment schedule sheet.</p>
