<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-cash-flow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="598"><p sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-cash-flow.md" sourcestartlinenumber="598">Select payment sources that should be moved to another date, or that should be paid by using another method of payment or payment account.</p>
